Enhanced Azure VM Terraform Module – Demo Documentation
1. Overview

This Terraform module provisions secure, enterprise-grade Azure Virtual Machines with advanced capabilities including:

Disk encryption

Monitoring and diagnostics

Backup and disaster recovery

Snapshot-based recovery

Network security

Identity management

Policy compliance

High availability

VM lifecycle management

The module supports both Windows and Linux VMs and integrates with Azure Monitor, Log Analytics, Recovery Services Vault, and Azure Policy.

